        <h2><a name="Become_a_Member"></a>Become a Member</h2>
        <table width="718" border="0" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0">
          <tr>
            <td width="358" valign="top"><table width="358" border="0" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0">
                <tr>
                  <td height="10"></td>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                  <td valign="top"><ul>
                      <li >To become a member, you can do one of the following:<br>
                        <ul>
                              <li>Visit our <a href="https://secure.clubpenguin.com/membership/">Become a Member</a> page. </li>
                                <li>From the Club Penguin home page, click &lsquo;Membership&rsquo; and follow the directions.</li>
                                <li>When you are logged in, click the settings button (question mark icon, far right), then click &lsquo;Become a Member&rsquo; and follow the instructions from there.</li>
                        </ul>
                      </ul></td>
              </tr>
            </table></td>
            <td width="10" valign="top">&nbsp;</td>
            <td width="350" valign="top"><img src="../../images/screenshots/become-member.gif" width="350" height="220"></td>
          </tr>
        </table>
       
