        </div>
		<h2><a name="Cancel_a_Membership"></a>Cancel a Membership</h2>
		<table width="718" border="0" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0">
          <tr>
            <td width="358" valign="top"><table width="358" border="0" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0">
                <tr>
                  <td height="10"></td>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                  <td>Membership cancellations only apply to monthly memberships purchased using a   credit card. These memberships automatically recur each month to ensure   uninterrupted membership service.<BR>
                      <BR>
You may cancel your membership at any   time. You will still receive the full membership period that you have purchased.<BR>
<BR>
Canceling a membership requires the penguin name and password. If you   don't know your password, please visit <a href="http://support.clubpenguin.com/lost-password.php">Forgot Password</a> to have it emailed   to you.</p>
                    <p>To cancel your account: </p>
                    <ul>
                      <li>Go to <a href="http://play.clubpenguin.com/edit.htm">edit your account</a>, enter your penguin name and password, then   select &ldquo;Cancel your membership&rdquo;.</li>
                      <li>Go to <a href="http://www.clubpenguin.com/">clubpenguin.com</a>, click on the   "Membership" tab, and select the option to cancel.</li>
                      </ul></td>
                </tr>
            </table></td>
            <td width="10" valign="top">&nbsp;</td>
            <td width="350" valign="top"><img src="../../images/screenshots/cancel-membership.gif" width="350" height="220"></td>
          </tr>
        </table>
		
		<div align="right"><a href="#top">back to top</a>
        </div>
		<h2><a name="Changing_Safe_Chat_Level"></a>Changing Safe Chat Level</h2>
		<table width="718" border="0" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0">
          <tr>
            <td width="358" valign="top"><table width="358" border="0" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0">
                <tr>
                  <td height="10"></td>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                  <td><ul>
                      <li> <img src="images/your-account-chat-safe-icon.gif" alt="Edit Account Button" width="48" height="48" align="right">To change safe chat level, login, and click the Edit Account button on the far right of the toolbar. <br>
                      </li>
                      <li> Check the box at the bottom that either says 'Ultimate Safe Chat Mode' or 'Standard Safe Chat Mode'.</li>
                      <li>If you chose to enter a parent password when you created your account, you will be asked to enter the password to continue. </li>
                      <li>Log off and re-enter the world. Your new settings will take effect when you re-enter. </li>
                      <li>If you are in Ultimate Safe Chat mode, you will only see Ultimate Safe Chat messages, as well as actions, emotes, and greeting cards.</li>
                      </ul></td>
                </tr>
            </table></td>
            <td width="10" valign="top">&nbsp;</td>
            <td width="350" valign="top"><img src="../../images/screenshots/change-safe-chat.gif" width="350" height="220"></td>
          </tr>
        </table>
		
		<div align="right"><a href="#top">back to top</a>
        </div>
		<h2><a name="Changing_Your_Password"></a>Changing Your Password</h2>
		<table width="718" border="0" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0">
          <tr>
            <td width="358" valign="top"><table width="358" border="0" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0">
                <tr>
                  <td height="10"></td>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                  <td align="left" valign="top"><img src="images/your-account-chat-safe-icon.gif" alt="Edit Account Button" width="48" height="48" align="right">To change your password, login, and click the Edit Account on the far right of the toolbar.
                    <ul>
       
	   
	    <li>Click on &ldquo;Change Your Password&rdquo;.</li>
        <li>Enter your old password and the new password in the spaces provided. </li>
        <li>Enter the email address you used to set up the account. </li>
        <li>If the change is successful, you will get a message that says &ldquo;Your password has been updated.&rdquo;</li>
        <li>The next time you login, use your new password.</li>
    </ul></td>
                </tr>
            </table></td>
            <td width="10" valign="top">&nbsp;</td>
            <td width="350" valign="top"><img src="../../images/screenshots/change-password.gif" width="350" height="220"></td>
          </tr>
        </table>
		
        <div align="right"><a href="#top">back to top<br>
        </a> </div>
        <h2><a name="Breaking_the_Rules"></a>Breaking the Rules</h2>
        <table width="718" border="0" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0">
          <tr>
            <td width="358" valign="top"><table width="358" border="0" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0">
                <tr>
                  <td height="10"></td>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                  <td height="80"><ul>
                      <li> If you swear, cheat, or say something that is against the rules, you will be banned. This means you will not be able to use your account for a period of time &ndash; anywhere from 24 hours to forever. </li>
                      <li> If you are a member and you are banned, you will <strong>not</strong> be reimbursed for the time that you were banned. </li>
                      <li> A ban can happen automatically, which takes effect instantly, or be assigned by a moderator, which may take a little more time. </li>
                  </ul></td>
                </tr>
            </table></td>
            <td width="10" valign="top">&nbsp;</td>
            <td width="350" valign="top"><img src="../../images/screenshots/breaking-rules.gif" width="350" height="220"></td>
          </tr>
        </table>
        <div align="right"><a href="#top">back to top</a> </div>
        <h2><a name="Banned_Penguin"></a>How a Penguin is Banned </h2>
        <table width="718" border="0" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0">
          <tr>
            <td width="358" valign="top"><table width="358" border="0" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0">
                <tr>
                  <td height="10"></td>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                  <td height="80"><p>A penguin can be banned either automatically or by a moderator. </p>
                      <ul>
                        <li> An Automatic Ban occurs instantly when the player has said one of several flagged bad words. </li>
                        <li> A Moderator Ban happens when: </li>
                        <ul>
                          <li> A player reports another player; </li>
                          <li>A record of all conversation at that time in that room is sent to the moderators, including filtered messages;</li>
                          <li>A moderator reviews the conversation;</li>
                          <li><strong>If</strong> the moderator sees bad language or inappropriate behavior, they will ban the guilty penguin 24 hours for a first-time offense or 72 hours for a second or third offense. </li>
                          <li> Four or more offenses may result in a permanent ban.</li>
                        </ul>
                    </ul></td>
                </tr>
            </table></td>
            <td width="10" valign="top">&nbsp;</td>
            <td width="350" valign="top"><img src="../../images/screenshots/banned-login.gif" width="350" height="220"></td>
          </tr>
        </table>
        <div align="right"><a href="#top">back to top</a> </div>
